{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act35side", "eventName": "太陽甩在身後", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "AS-ST-2", "avgTag": "幕間", "storyName": "甦醒的城市", "storyInfo": "從獸主口中，祖拜爾得知它們一直在等候自己回歸，而一旁的拉恕爾也奉上了另一顆寶石。此刻，祖拜爾徹底回憶起自己的身分與職責——作為沙阿的將領守護沙阿留下的輝煌寶藏。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$wasteland_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "53_g8_sargondeluxeroom", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#4$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4058_pepe_1#8$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看起來祖拜爾似乎是打破了窗戶……自己離開了？", "name": "阿娜特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#4$1"}, {"id": 14, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4058_pepe_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我會去把他找回來的。", "name": "佩佩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#8$1"}, {"id": 16, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "交給博物館去找吧，佩佩，你已經很多天都沒好好休息了。", "name": "阿娜特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#1$1"}, {"id": 18, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4058_pepe_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "黃金之城的使者很快就會抵達父親的領地，阿娜特，我必須把握每一秒。", "name": "佩佩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#8$1"}, {"id": 20, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "佩佩……", "name": "阿娜特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#9$1"}, {"id": 22, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4058_pepe_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博物館的損壞辛苦你和緹緹收拾了，或許有幾個地方祖拜爾會去，我這就出發。", "name": "佩佩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#8$1"}, {"id": 24, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "佩佩，你知道我為何一開始不願將祖拜爾借給你研究嗎？其實收到你的來信後，我就想告訴你了……", "name": "阿娜特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#1$1"}, {"id": 26, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在兩個月前，我去你父親的領地出差，在那裡我見到黃金之城的使者已經抵達。", "name": "阿娜特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#2$1"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的弟弟已經出發了。", "name": "阿娜特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#2$1"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4058_pepe_1#12$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "佩佩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#12$1"}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你知道，但你卻沒有告訴我。", "name": "佩佩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#12$1"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你在信中興高采烈地向我描述你的發現，在裡面連寫了二十個驚嘆號來表達自己的興奮。", "name": "阿娜特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#2$1"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#10$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我……我實在是不忍心。", "name": "阿娜特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#10$1"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4058_pepe_1#12$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你為什麼又要把他借給我，你讓我白高興一場……", "name": "佩佩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#12$1"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡是寶石之城，佩佩！這裡的寶石數不勝數，我以為你根本不可能找到！", "name": "阿娜特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#2$1"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想著，或許時間一到你自己就放棄了。", "name": "阿娜特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#2$1"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4058_pepe_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但……但黃金之城的使者一直都是八月份才會到的啊？為什麼會提前？", "name": "佩佩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#8$1"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你父親上書，希望使者提前到來。", "name": "阿娜特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#1$1"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4058_pepe_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以他們早就做好了決定，只是怕我不甘心，才趁我離開家尋找沙阿遺跡的時候，將那小子送入黃金之城。", "name": "佩佩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#8$1"}, {"id": 47, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 15.0, "ystrength": 15.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4058_pepe_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但父親不是和我說……他會等著看到我的發現再做決斷嗎？", "name": "佩佩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#9$1"}, {"id": 50, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "佩佩，長輩總是有自己的決斷，不是我們這些小輩能插手的。", "name": "阿娜特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#9$1"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4058_pepe_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你見到那小子了嗎？", "name": "佩佩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#8$1"}, {"id": 54, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……嗯。", "name": "阿娜特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#9$1"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4058_pepe_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他一定很得意吧，為了進入黃金之城，我與他不知道明裡暗裡較量過多少次。", "name": "佩佩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#3$1"}, {"id": 58, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "佩佩，你弟弟並不開心，我看得出，他的神色中始終隱藏著憂傷。", "name": "阿娜特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#9$1"}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那天，他將我叫到書房，說自己知道這輩子和你再也不會有見面的機會，希望我能帶句話給你。", "name": "阿娜特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#9$1"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4058_pepe_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他說了什麼？", "name": "佩佩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#8$1"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他說他希望你能記得他的聲音。說完後，他便離開了。", "name": "阿娜特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#9$1"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他行李很少，而其中只有幾樣是他的，剩下的，全部與你和伯父有關。", "name": "阿娜特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#9$1"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4058_pepe_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "佩佩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#5$1"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "佩佩……？", "name": "阿娜特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#1$1"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4058_pepe_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從小到大，所有人都和我說，成為陛下身邊的史官是為整個家族延續榮耀。但是阿娜特，榮耀往往是用犧牲與奉獻換來的。", "name": "佩佩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#5$1"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "進入黃金之城成為史官，意味著要終身留在城中，再也不能與家人朋友相見，能夠陪伴在身邊的，只有無數的書卷。", "name": "佩佩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#5$1"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你最厭惡成日枯坐在書桌前了……不是嗎，佩佩？", "name": "阿娜特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#2$1"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4058_pepe_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊，我也想在有生之年走遍薩爾貢，自由自在地尋訪每一處歷史留下的痕跡。", "name": "佩佩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#2$1"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4058_pepe_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我不能這樣……因為我不能讓那小子得償所願。", "name": "佩佩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#8$1"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "佩佩，你就這麼看不慣你弟弟嗎？寧可自己難受也不能讓他順遂心意。", "name": "阿娜特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#9$1"}, {"id": 81, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4058_pepe_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從小到大，誰見到那小子都會誇一句，說他性格文靜又沉穩，是做史官的人才。", "name": "佩佩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#8$1"}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只有我才清楚，他本性有多調皮多貪玩，讓他在桌子前多坐一秒都是折磨。", "name": "佩佩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#8$1"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那他和你爭史官的位置是為了什麼？", "name": "阿娜特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#5$1"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4058_pepe_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因為他不想要我去黃金之城。", "name": "佩佩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#2$1"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他只是不想要我一個人留在那裡……", "name": "佩佩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#2$1"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你……？", "name": "阿娜特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#1$1"}, {"id": 91, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4058_pepe_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我也是……", "name": "佩佩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#5$1"}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我也不想要他一個人留在那裡。", "name": "佩佩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#5$1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "53_g12_gemexchange", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_open_woodbox", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1479_1#1$1", "duration": 0.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "緩解站立過久導致的腿酸的寶石？不是這個。", "name": "祖拜爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1479_1#1$1"}, {"id": 106, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_jewelryimpact", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "讓對方主動道歉的寶石？有點用，但也不是我要找的。", "name": "祖拜爾"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1479_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我能感覺到那一顆寶石十分接近，但這間屋子裡的寶石也太多了吧……", "name": "祖拜爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1479_1#4$1"}, {"id": 112, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_pawfootstep_1", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_pawfootstep_3", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$ponder_intro", "key": "$ponder_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聽到走廊中傳來的腳步聲，祖拜爾立刻慌忙地躺回到巨大的鍍金箱子裡。"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他感覺到了目光的注視，然而沒有聲音打破這一陣沉默，他忐忑地將眼睛睜開一條縫——"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是一隻沙色的動物。"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_pawfootstep_3", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1482_1#6$1", "posfrom": "-200,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_meowlong", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1482_1#1$1", "duration": 0.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "噢……不可思議……", "name": "祖拜爾"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_cakebgflgrnd", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1482_1#7$1", "duration": 0.2}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "action": "jump", "posto": "200,150", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "power": 20.0, "times": 1.0, "duration": 0.8}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.3}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沙色的動物跳進了鍍金箱子裡，臉貼著祖拜爾的金面具，似乎在輕嗅著其中散發的氣味。"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "黑色的動物也把頭探了進來。"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_pawfootstep_2", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1483_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_bellshake", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1479_1#1$1", "posfrom": "0,-20", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "米奧……沃奧……？", "name": "祖拜爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1479_1#1$1"}, {"id": 148, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1482_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看來，你的記憶已經恢復得差不多了。", "name": "米奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1482_1#1$1"}, {"id": 150, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1483_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，味道不會錯，你不是贗品。", "name": "沃奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1483_1#1$1"}, {"id": 152, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1482_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "閉嘴吧沃奧。", "name": "米奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1482_1#4$1"}, {"id": 154, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1479_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們怎麼變得這麼小了……？", "name": "祖拜爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1479_1#1$1"}, {"id": 156, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1482_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們變成現在的樣子，還不是因為你沒有盡到僕從的職責？", "name": "米奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1482_1#4$1"}, {"id": 158, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1479_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "僕從的職責……", "name": "祖拜爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1479_1#3$1"}, {"id": 160, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1482_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果我在你們的眼裡還是過去的樣貌，那我就得天天被抬出去遊行，哪有時間幫你找寶石？", "name": "米奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1482_1#4$1"}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "相比之下，還是現在的形態更方便。", "name": "米奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1482_1#4$1"}, {"id": 163, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1483_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "米奧，現在的祖拜爾還無法理解我們在討論的內容。", "name": "沃奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1483_1#1$1"}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在他到來之前，我已經告誡過你了。", "name": "沃奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1483_1#1$1"}, {"id": 166, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_meowlong", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1482_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（憤怒地瞪視）哼……", "name": "米奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1482_1#5$1"}, {"id": 169, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1483_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（心虛地迴避）", "name": "沃奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1483_1#1$1"}, {"id": 171, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1482_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒關係，祖拜爾馬上就會明白，這三百年來我們都經歷了什麼。", "name": "米奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1482_1#5$1"}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沃奧，去把我們的新僕從叫來吧。", "name": "米奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1482_1#5$1"}, {"id": 174, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "53_g12_gemexchange", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_openftstpwalk"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "年輕的監管人穿過長長的走廊，走到祖拜爾的面前。"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_wing"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "藍色的羽獸倏然飛起，飛向交易所牆壁的高處，撥動鑲嵌其上的機關。"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "齒輪嚙合，發條喀喀作響，羽獸從開啟的保險櫃中取出了一顆寶石。"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "羽獸將寶石放在托盤上的深褐色絨布中央，由年輕的監管人呈上。"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他的目光平和，他的目光熾熱。"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_openftstpwalk", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4140_lasher_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "祖拜爾先生，初次見面……不，好久不見。", "name": "拉恕爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4140_lasher_1#1$1"}, {"id": 194, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4140_lasher_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這顆寶石是我的砝碼。", "name": "拉恕爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4140_lasher_1#3$1"}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "附加上這間寶石交易所，還有在大巴扎流通的所有寶石……", "name": "拉恕爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4140_lasher_1#3$1"}, {"id": 197, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4140_lasher_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "祖拜爾先生，我想知道這些全部加起來，能否比一個罪人的靈魂更沉重？", "name": "拉恕爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4140_lasher_1#10$1"}, {"id": 199, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "35_g18_deserttown_n", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "Blocker", "attribut